{"tid":320051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好丈夫返工捱到殘 仲要俾個死婆趕出廳瞓 含怒入眠最終暴斃","createTime":"2017-07-13T09:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T03:58:51.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":336,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78fb43f93f152bb8cf3784a330294436770e15a3","tid":320051,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:07:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170712/56944227\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170712%2F56944227&d=CcwWB%2B7%2BJiuzxBP24F9pkv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=a727b3f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170712%2F56944227&h=376a3aea\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170712/56944227</a><br />\n<br />\n英國一名女子不滿丈夫工作時間太長<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，與「捱到殘」的丈夫大吵一場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，還趕他出廳睡梳化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，翌晨竟發現丈夫暴斃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。更慘的是，她發現丈夫辛勞工作，原來是為了儲錢帶她去旅行慶祝結婚周年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170712/large/1499804614_f986.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170712%2Flarge%2F1499804614_f986.jpg&h=8ebe3fd2&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"5265cf270b60644eefbd4c3112aaaa66589aeeea","tid":320051,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d5fa8cd5a4554877d6bd3e001c9b9b93eaec9d","tid":320051,"uid":51920,"like":2,"dislike":196,"score":-194,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:08:59.000Z","msg":"阿什莉又說，人生苦短，無必要帶怒入夢。阿什莉的朋友透露，阿什莉喪夫後，獲小叔克里斯（Chris）支持度過悲痛時刻，兩人火速發展出戀情。"},{"pid":"3ac7c1f5f6bc57f556c48df625e77c8a6fc48f82","tid":320051,"uid":126165,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:09:07.000Z","msg":"閪女人"},{"pid":"9cd88023c17959b96592bdda0a883e5df75ec768","tid":320051,"uid":26451,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:09:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a509e2c6a41d86880006d0bbb5afece6511777b6","tid":320051,"uid":14497,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:10:03.000Z","msg":"阿什莉又說，人生苦短，無必要帶怒入夢。阿什莉的朋友透露，阿什莉喪夫後，獲小叔克里斯（Chris）支持度過悲痛時刻，兩人火速發展出戀情。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"443b1db4716e2465c6711c9a79c6e4e09b0fa5e5","tid":320051,"uid":1886,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:10:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170712/large/1499804613_df05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170712%2Flarge%2F1499804613_df05.jpg&h=d6e9f875&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n阿什莉（Ashley Murrel）與36歲丈夫默雷爾（Mikey Murrell）結婚七年，育有三孩。默雷爾任職地氈清潔員，死前經常超時工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，每晚回家筋疲力盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不似人形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。5月16日，默雷爾經過16小時工作後，又帶着一臉倦容回家，阿什莉不滿丈夫只顧工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，忍無可忍之下與他吵架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，當晚還趕他去睡梳化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。翌晨，阿什莉發現丈夫毫無反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，臉如死灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，原來已經暴斃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n驗屍結果顯示，默雷爾因在睡夢中窒息死亡，背後原因未能確定。<br />\n<br />\n阿什莉後來發現，丈夫日忙夜忙，七天無休，無非要賺夠錢，7月3日結婚周年時請她去布拉格旅行慶祝。她說：「我很內疚。我怨自己趕他出廳睡梳化。我仍接受不到對他最後說的竟是惡言。」但她也指丈夫工作時間太長，「總是筋疲力倦，他的健康也急速變差」。<br />\n<br />\n阿什莉又說，人生苦短，無必要帶怒入夢。阿什莉的朋友透露，阿什莉喪夫後，<span style=\"color: red;\">獲小叔克里斯（Chris）支持度過悲痛時刻，兩人火速發展出戀情<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</span>"},{"pid":"eb7b99bfca99ad7ba01327deb56f99e69cc68e5b","tid":320051,"uid":63669,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eccb30217a88242bd54ff153bbf19bd8c8b5d73a","tid":320051,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:12:52.000Z","msg":"未亡人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc77112a5eac9182cb132bcb5f5d7d3ac1da6eb3","tid":320051,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:13:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170712/large/1499804613_df05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https